  von Gagern in bug #407301

*haskell-updater-1.2.0.5-r1 (09 Apr 2012)

  09 Apr 2012; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  +haskell-updater-1.2.0.5-r1.ebuild, -haskell-updater-1.2.0.3.ebuild:
  Force linkage against ghc's Cabal library. That way we make sure h-u will not
  fail to build when Cabal is already installed, but broken.

  04 Apr 2012; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  haskell-updater-1.2.0.5.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/ppc/sparc stable wrt bug #407835

